The '''Metropolis Razer''' was a model of [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]] which stood two meters tall. [[2X-NM]] was one such [[Droid/Legends|droid]], although he was modified to become a short order cook by [[Mother (suspected smuggler)|Mother]] for [[Mother's]].

